---
_i describe the stack_

_i allow for parameters, every coffin should just require parameters
---

```
Here lies <Some_Stack_name>
<Some description>
```
- first line "Here Lies" is optional
- second line is description

# this could be a prompt, with ascii/ansi art
```
Here lies <Some_Stack_name>
<Some description>
    <one line>

known for <some_param> being <some_arg> 
[mappings]
```

